{
  "stem": "25651.7",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I wonder how many of the grownups got the message when the jam and the margarine and the cheese-- it was sort of ersatz cheese, but nevertheless it was fat, and it was nourishing-- when that was done away with and you only had the bread without anything, whether people drew the right conclusion from that.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, because the camp was liquidated.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I certainly didn't draw that conclusion at the time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I remember that I did not draw the conclusion.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I only-- I was too busy trying to steal food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were all Czech.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the-- that was all Theresienstadt stuff.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the Germans were in charge.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were kapos.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was the lageralteste, who was a political German prisoner who was a prisoner from a prison who, presumably, volunteered to be in charge of a camp of 10,000 people.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was in this Jugendheim.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And these Red Cross parcels arrived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By the time that the Red Cross parcels arrived, lots of people who had asked for parcels [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] had already died of natural causes, because within six months-- I now read this.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't know then-- but I now read that a third of us died within six months, of natural causes.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Just because of the privation of cold and mud, and standing in the mud, you know, to these appels.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I remember the first appel, that morning that I was describing to you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Sure fantastic scene.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was standing next to a man, and he was clutching in his hand a syringe and insulin.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I asked him, you know, what's this for?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So he said, this is my last insulin.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Tomorrow I'll die.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But he had a half open vial.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
